Wild Bill Elliott https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wild_Bill_Elliott 0 Wild Bill Elliott (October 16, 1904 – November 26, 1965) was an American film actor. He specialized in playing the rugged heroes of B Westerns, particularly the Red Ryder series of films. Wild_Bill_Elliott ( October_16_,_1904 – November_26_,_1965 ) was an_American_film_actor .
